              💡 Innovación FP 2019/20
            </a>
            <a href="/curso2020-2021" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-green-600 block px-3 py-2 text-sm">
              🌍 Impacto ESO/FP 2020/21
            </a>
            <a href="/curso2021-2022" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-green-600 block px-3 py-2 text-sm">
              🎯 Resultados ESO/BAT/FP 2021/22
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/#mentor-benefits" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 block px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          ⭐ ¿Por qué ser Mentor?
        </a>
        
        <a href="/partners" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 block px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          🏢 Organizaciones
        </a>
        
        <a href="/blog" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 block px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
          📝 Blog
        </a>
        
